[[File:Authority on Radio (logo).png|right]]

'''AOR, Ltd.''' (''Authority on Radio Communications, Ltd.'') is a [[Japan]]ese based manufacturer of [[radio]] equipment, including [[Two-way radio|transceiver]]s, [[Scanner (radio)|scanner]]s, [[Antenna (radio)|antenna]]s and frequency monitors.

Established in 1977 when two radio amateurs decided to go professional. Based in [[Tokyo]], [[Japan]], they also have offices in the [[United Kingdom]] and the [[United States]], and manufacturing facilities in Japan and the United Kingdom.

